  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f7c7181&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUBWAWibiaa4jcHY3SlFa6DgbW6wicWgn9aDnOBOMc4H5MG29YmOJuicibj5GNRE4Dldz1Rt5sYt3bHqqmNxggjM7tiaQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在AGI的探索中，我们再次突破大模型的能力边界。</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">作为GLM系列的最新版本，GLM-4.6是我们最强的代码Coding模型（</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">较GLM-4.5提升27%</span><span textstyle=\"\">）。在真实编程、长上下文处理、推理能力、信息搜索、写作能力与智能体应用等多个方面实现全面提升。如下：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">高级编</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">码能力</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\">在公开基准与真实编程任务中，GLM-4.6的代码能力</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">对齐Claude Sonnet 4</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">，是国内已知的最好的Coding模型。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">上下</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">文长度</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：<span textstyle=\"\">上下文窗口由</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">128K→200K</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">，<span textstyle=\"\">适应更长的代码和智能体任务。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">推理能力</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">推理能力提升，并支持在推理过程中调用工具</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">搜索能力</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">增强模型的工具调用和搜索智能体，在智能体框架中表现更好。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">写作能力</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：<span textstyle=\"\">在文风、可读性与角色扮演场景中更符合人类偏好。</span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM-4.6</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">已</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">上</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">线</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">智谱MaaS平台</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">bigmodel.cn</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">，<span textstyle=\"\">即将在Hugging Face、ModelScope</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开源</span><span textstyle=\"\">，遵循MIT协议。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coding能力创国产模型新高</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:0px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;list-style:none;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">1.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">综合评测</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">8大权威基准</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">：AIME 25、LCB v6、HLE、SWE-Bench Verified、BrowseComp、Terminal-Bench、τ^2-Bench、GPQA 模型通用能力的评估中，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-4.6在部分</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">榜单表现</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">对齐</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Claude Sonnet 4/Claude Sonnet 4.5</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">，</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">稳居国产模型首位。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg66ntoi135j\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyHgMEq37FfNpEOWQJGSEsY780tJLaDqQibK6kXu9nUJK3tIuicdHhzicAibQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"457\" data-imgfileid=\"100008343\" data-ratio=\"0.7816666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2400\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2f9dc19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyHgMEq37FfNpEOWQJGSEsY780tJLaDqQibK6kXu9nUJK3tIuicdHhzicAibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ol style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:0px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;list-style:none;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#1679ff;font-weight:bold;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">2.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">真实编程评测</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">为了测试模型在实际编程任务中的能力，我们在</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Claude Code环境</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">下进行了</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">74个真实场景编程任务测试。</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">结果显示</span>，</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM-4.6实测超过Claude Sonnet 4，超越其他国产模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg596ngk1j2y\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100008337\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48515625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyH6rhGvI5FcA4U7I7KPot2d28Q8277YmyaYoJibK4nRETulpsiaLiaLJuiag/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f97f94a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyH6rhGvI5FcA4U7I7KPot2d28Q8277YmyaYoJibK4nRETulpsiaLiaLJuiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在平均token消耗上，GLM-4.6比GLM-4.5节省</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">30%以上</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">，为同类模型最低。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:12px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg596zvkm7a\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyHkC9FXUjGa7A3wjd7qWfWSaadSoh4WZtrUk1CgaFn49qzn7UC9xnLwA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"576\" data-cropsely2=\"276\" data-imgfileid=\"100008338\" data-ratio=\"0.48046875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f60e5e55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUBWAWibiaa4jf1PM7wKj7RgC0p61QN8qyHkC9FXUjGa7A3wjd7qWfWSaadSoh4WZtrUk1CgaFn49qzn7UC9xnLwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">为确保透明性与可信度，智谱已公开全部测试题目与Agent轨迹，供业界验证与复现</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">（</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);\">链接</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/zai-org/CC-Bench-trajectories\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/zai-org/CC-Bench-trajectories</a></span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">）</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">适配寒武纪、摩尔</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">线程</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">芯片</span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM-4.6已在寒武纪领先的国产芯片上实现FP8+Int4混合量化部署，这是首次在国产芯片投产的FP8+Int4模型芯片一体解决方案，</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">在保持精度不变的前提下，大幅降低推理成本，为国产芯片在大模型本地化运行上开创了可行路径。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">基于vLLM推理框架部署，摩尔线程新一代GPU可基于原生FP8精度稳定运行GLM-4.6，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">充分印证了MUSA架构和全功能GPU在生态兼容与快速支持方面的强大优势。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM-4.6和寒武纪、摩尔线程国产芯片的组合，即将通过智谱MaaS平台正式面向大众和企业提供服务。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">未来，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">国产原创GLM大模型与</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">国产芯片</span><span textstyle=\"\">将</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">联合推动在模型训练和推理环节的性能与效率优化。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Coding Plan 全面升级</span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">随着GLM-4.6发布，智谱同步升级</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM Coding Plan（最低20元包月畅玩套餐）</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">同时推出</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM Coding Plan企业版套餐</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">，为企业级用</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">户提供兼具</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">安全、成本效益与国际顶尖性能</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">的编码套餐。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">此前订阅</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">GLM Coding Plan包月套餐</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">的用户</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">自动升级至</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-4.6，</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">新增：</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">图像识别与搜索能力。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">支持</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">Claude Code、Roo Code、Kilo Code、Cline</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">等10+主流编程工具。</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">面向高频重度开发者提供</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">GLM Coding Max</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">，是Claude Max (20x) plan三倍用量。</span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">获取与体验</span></h2>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">智谱MaaS平台</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">bigmodel.cn、</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">z.ai</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">、</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">智谱清言</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">已全面支持GLM-4.6；</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">海外用户</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">可通过</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">z.ai</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">使用 API；</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">开源部署</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">：GLM-4.6模型将在</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">Hugging Face、ModelScope</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">发布；</span></span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">开发者和企业通过bigmodel.cn直接购买GLM Coding Plan套餐/企业版套餐。</span></span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM-4.6的上一代模型GLM-4.5首次在单个模型中实现将推理、编码和智能体能力原生融合。GLM-4.5在代码能力上的突出表现让其取得一些成绩，在OpenRouter上稳居全球前十供应商，自发布后智谱MaaS平台API商业化实现10倍以上增长。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">更多资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">GLM-4.6 技术博客：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://z.ai/blog/glm-4.6\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/blog/glm-4.6</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布旗舰代码模型 GLM-4.6，在代码能力上取得显著提升，支持国产芯片部署，并推出升级版商业套餐。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布旗舰代码模型 GLM-4.6，在代码能力上取得显著提升，支持国产芯片部署，并推出升级版商业套餐。",
  "summary": "文章宣布了智谱最新旗舰代码模型 GLM-4.6 的上线，强调其在代码能力上的全面进阶，较 GLM-4.5 提升 27%。GLM-4.6 在高级编码、长上下文处理（200K）、推理、搜索和写作能力方面均有提升，并在公开基准测试和真实编程任务中表现优异，部分榜单对齐 Claude Sonnet 4，被誉为国内最佳代码模型。文章还指出 GLM-4.6 在平均 token 消耗上比上一代节省 30%以上，并首次在寒武纪和摩尔线程等国产芯片上实现 FP8+Int4 混合量化部署，为国产芯片在大模型本地化运行开创了可行路径。智谱同步升级了 GLM Coding Plan，提供个人和企业版套餐，并公开了部分测试数据以供业界验证。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.6 在代码能力上实现显著突破，成为国产最佳代码模型。",
      "explanation": "在多个权威基准和真实编程任务中，GLM-4.6 表现对齐甚至超越 Claude Sonnet 4，并大幅提升上下文长度和推理能力，为开发者提供更强的代码辅助。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.6 优化了资源效率并适配国产硬件，推动 AI 生态发展。",
      "explanation": "模型平均 token 消耗降低 30%以上，并首次在寒武纪、摩尔线程等国产芯片上实现高效混合量化部署，有效降低推理成本，支持国产 AI 软硬件协同。"
    },
    {
      "point": "智谱通过升级商业套餐，加速模型商业化与开发者生态建设。",
      "explanation": "推出个人和企业版 GLM Coding Plan，提供更强的 API 服务和编程工具支持，旨在吸引更广泛的开发者和企业用户，促进模型应用落地。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "GLM-4.6 是我们最强的代码 Coding 模型（较 GLM-4.5 提升 27%）。",
